item.title: Jebsen Group marks six decades of collaboration with Porsche by celebrating their 60th anniversary
item.description: Source: Jebsen Group. Pictured from left: Grant Smith, General Manager of Porsche Centre Hong Kong and Macau; Franz Jung, President and CEO of Porsche China; Hans Joachim Stuck, two-time winner of the 24 Hours of Le Mans; Hans Michael Jebsen, Chairman of Jebsen Group; Helmuth Hennig, Group Managing Director of Jebsen Group; Earl Anderson Bamber, 2015 champion of the 24 Hours of Le Mans; and Joachim Eberlein, Managing Director of Jebsen Motors.
